# 🔄 7. Arbeiten mit Git in Eclipse

## 📥 Vor der Arbeit

```
Team → Switch To → main
Team → Pull
Team → Switch To → New Branch
```

## 💾 Commit

```
Team → Commit
```

## 📤 Push

```
Team → Push
```

oder:

```
Commit and Push
```

